Beautiful, trendy, comfortable clothes.
Loved!

SERRV has incredible, hand-crafted, fairly-traded items ranging from clothing to hand-woven baskets to linens.
Most recently I stopped in and checked out the gorgeous baskets which range in size and are all very unique.
It's a super cool non-profit org that supports communities around the world and works to eradicate poverty.
Awesome place to shop and support a good cause while doin' it.

